fields.description:
h5.Steps to reproduce:
1. Make sure you have {{ti.admob}} ver.3.0.1 & {{ti.map}} ver.3.0.1 in your tiapp.xml.
2. Build for android device/emulator.

h5.Actual results:
1. The build fails with:
{code}[ERROR] :  jarsigner: unable to sign jar: java.util.zip.ZipException: duplicate entry: org/appcelerator/titanium/gen/bindings.json{code}

h5.Expected results:
1. The build should be successful.
fields.summary: Android: java.util.zip.ZipException: duplicate entry: org/appcelerator/titanium/gen/bindings.json when having both ti.admob & ti.map modules in the project
